## 4) Switching to the Coding Plan endpoint

If you’re specifically using the **GLM Coding Plan**, swap baseURL to:
`https://api.z.ai/api/coding/paas/v4` ([Z.AI][2])

With the community provider:

```ts
import { createZhipu } from 'zhipu-ai-provider';

export const zaiCoding = createZhipu({
  baseURL: 'https://api.z.ai/api/coding/paas/v4',
  apiKey: process.env.ZHIPU_API_KEY!,
});
```

Then:

```ts
model: zaiCoding('glm-4.7')
```

